1
00:00:50,049 --> 00:00:52,469
DRAMA INI HANYA REKAAN

2
00:00:52,552 --> 00:00:54,971
RAKAMAN MEMATUHI GARIS PANDUAN

3
00:01:01,895 --> 00:01:06,316
SHIN I-RANG, HAN NA-HYUN
FIRMA GUAMAN

4
00:01:16,117 --> 00:01:18,453
Boleh saya bantu?

5
00:01:20,038 --> 00:01:21,164
Mak cik!

6
00:01:26,127 --> 00:01:29,339
Patutlah dah lama tak nampak mak cik.

7
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,258
Mak cik dah meninggal?

8
00:01:35,011 --> 00:01:37,806
Sudahlah mak cik hidup susah,
kemudian mati begini pula.

9
00:01:39,474 --> 00:01:41,226
- Aduh!
- Kamu merepek apa?

10
00:01:41,810 --> 00:01:44,145
Mak cik belum mati.

11
00:01:46,856 --> 00:01:49,526
- Aduh.
- Mak cik belum mati!

12
00:01:50,860 --> 00:01:52,153
Terima kasih.

13
00:01:52,237 --> 00:01:53,571
Terima kasih banyak-banyak.

14
00:01:53,655 --> 00:01:56,658
Kamu cakap bukan-bukan saja.

15
00:01:56,741 --> 00:01:57,617
Sudahlah.

16
00:01:57,700 --> 00:01:59,828
Awal awak datang. Saya belikan kopi.

17
00:02:01,204 --> 00:02:02,664
Helo.

18
00:02:02,747 --> 00:02:03,915
Aduhai.

19
00:02:06,084 --> 00:02:07,293
Saya pun nampak dia.

20
00:02:07,377 --> 00:02:08,920
Peguam Han, ini…

21
00:02:14,175 --> 00:02:16,052
Saya boleh sentuh dia juga.

22
00:02:17,220 --> 00:02:19,681
Mestilah boleh. Dia bukan hantu.

23
00:02:21,266 --> 00:02:22,183
Bukan?

24
00:02:22,267 --> 00:02:25,145
Aduh, kamu nak sangat mak cik mati?

25
00:02:25,228 --> 00:02:27,522
- Maaf.
- Maaf, mak cik.

26
00:02:28,690 --> 00:02:30,859
Mak cik, kita duduk dulu?

27
00:02:30,942 --> 00:02:32,068
Ya.

28
00:02:39,868 --> 00:02:40,910
Siapa dia?

29
00:02:41,452 --> 00:02:43,913
Dia kawan lama saya.

30
00:02:46,291 --> 00:02:48,793
Apa halnya mak cik ke sini?

31
00:02:48,877 --> 00:02:51,713
Mak cik nak jumpa kamu sebab kamu peguam.

32
00:02:51,796 --> 00:02:52,755
Kenapa?

33
00:02:52,839 --> 00:02:54,799
Mak cik ada masalah?

34
00:02:56,801 --> 00:02:58,386
Tak, bukan masalah itu.

35
00:02:59,262 --> 00:03:01,472
Ini sebab mendiang suami mak cik.

36
00:03:11,149 --> 00:03:15,612
Mendiang suami mak cik
berambut putih, berkening lebat

37
00:03:18,031 --> 00:03:19,115
dan kacak?

38
00:03:19,198 --> 00:03:20,325
Aduhai.

39
00:03:21,284 --> 00:03:24,078
Orang kata peguam di sini
dah macam psikik.

40
00:03:24,162 --> 00:03:25,705
Betullah kata orang.

41
00:03:26,289 --> 00:03:28,333
Peguam tak perlukan kuasa psikik.

42
00:03:28,416 --> 00:03:30,668
Sakitnya kepala!

43
00:03:33,630 --> 00:03:37,383
Suami mak cik ada penyakit?

44
00:03:37,967 --> 00:03:38,927
Ada.

45
00:03:39,802 --> 00:03:41,012
Dia ada Alzheimer.

46
00:03:43,139 --> 00:03:46,392
Sekali-sekala dia sedar siapa dia.

47
00:03:47,143 --> 00:03:50,438
Tapi selalunya,
dia cuma ingat zaman muda dia.

48
00:03:51,022 --> 00:03:52,148
Mak cik memang tabah.

49
00:04:02,200 --> 00:04:06,955
Mendiang suami mak cik suka kasut?

50
00:04:07,038 --> 00:04:09,540
Macam mana kamu tahu?

51
00:04:09,624 --> 00:04:12,126
Dia tukang kasut.

52
00:04:14,629 --> 00:04:16,965
Masa kami mula-mula jumpa dulu pun,

53
00:04:18,174 --> 00:04:20,134
dia dah buat kasut.

54
00:04:21,761 --> 00:04:23,137
TAHUN 1979

55
00:04:24,973 --> 00:04:27,684
Dia biadab dengan aku.

56
00:04:27,767 --> 00:04:30,186
<i>- Waktu itu…</i>
- Aku pun…

57
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:33,815
<i>…Seoul macam bandar ajaib</i>
<i>yang semuanya berubah semalaman.</i>

58
00:04:33,898 --> 00:04:37,568
<i>Mak cik ada banyak</i>
<i>impian besar semasa muda.</i>

59
00:04:37,652 --> 00:04:39,696
Tapi dia pelajar perubatan
Universiti Hanguk.

60
00:04:39,779 --> 00:04:41,864
Bukankah elok dibuat suami?

61
00:04:42,448 --> 00:04:44,325
Apa gunanya kalau elok dibuat suami?

62
00:04:44,409 --> 00:04:45,994
Aku juga yang jadi terbaik nanti.

63
00:04:47,287 --> 00:04:48,871
Sudahlah kau.

64
00:04:50,581 --> 00:04:52,500
Sayangnya.

65
00:04:52,583 --> 00:04:55,670
Dia paling sesuai jadi suami kau.

66
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:58,715
Kau tengok apa?

67
00:05:00,675 --> 00:05:02,135
Nanti aku tinggal.

68
00:05:03,344 --> 00:05:04,929
Hebatnya dia.

69
00:05:23,197 --> 00:05:24,282
Cik nak beli kasut baru?

70
00:05:25,074 --> 00:05:25,908
Apa?

71
00:05:26,492 --> 00:05:28,870
Kedai kami di sebelah. Ini bengkel kasut.

72
00:05:28,953 --> 00:05:30,288
Saya tahu.

73
00:05:30,955 --> 00:05:33,416
Saya bukan nak kasut baru.

74
00:05:37,462 --> 00:05:38,880
Saya nak awak.

75
00:05:40,590 --> 00:05:44,844
<i>Ketika itu, mak cik memang</i>
<i>nak buka kedai sendiri</i>

76
00:05:44,927 --> 00:05:47,472
<i>dengan duit kahwin yang mak ayah berikan</i>

77
00:05:47,555 --> 00:05:50,308
<i>selepas tamat pengajian</i>
<i>di akademi fesyen terkenal.</i>

78
00:05:50,892 --> 00:05:53,478
Kasut yang seronok dipakai.

79
00:05:54,145 --> 00:05:57,065
Rasa macam nak pergi
ke tempat seronok kalau pakai kasut itu.

80
00:05:58,399 --> 00:06:01,694
Kasut terbaik yang dibuat dengan ikhlas.

81
00:06:01,778 --> 00:06:03,112
Itulah impian mak cik.

82
00:06:03,654 --> 00:06:05,615
KASUT RIA

83
00:06:07,658 --> 00:06:11,204
Duit atau kepakaran saja
tak cukup untuk buat kasut terbaik.

84
00:06:11,871 --> 00:06:14,957
Tanpa kulit berkualiti,
takkan ada kasut terbaik.

85
00:06:15,041 --> 00:06:17,585
Saya tahu kulit berkualiti pun penting.

86
00:06:18,544 --> 00:06:20,213
Awak nak kulit syarikat mana?

87
00:06:21,130 --> 00:06:22,256
Kulit import?

88
00:06:23,633 --> 00:06:25,718
Itali? Perancis?

89
00:06:30,765 --> 00:06:32,391
Saya nak awak jumpa seseorang.

90
00:06:37,063 --> 00:06:38,898
<i>Seon Hwa orang Hamgyong, Korea Utara.</i>

91
00:06:38,981 --> 00:06:41,234
- Seon Hwa.
<i>- Dia gilap kulit seorang diri.</i>

92
00:06:41,317 --> 00:06:43,986
<i>Tak ada orang tolong dia.</i>

93
00:06:44,070 --> 00:06:47,907
<i>Kulit gilapan dia lembut macam</i>
<i>bulu pelepah, tapi kuat macam logam.</i>

94
00:06:47,990 --> 00:06:50,701
<i>Mak cik terus jatuh cinta</i>
<i>dengan hasil kerja dia.</i>

95
00:06:50,785 --> 00:06:51,994
KASUT IDEAL

96
00:06:52,078 --> 00:06:53,412
Jangan gementar.

97
00:06:54,288 --> 00:06:55,748
Relaks, semua.

98
00:06:55,832 --> 00:06:58,042
Satu, dua, tiga.

99
00:07:00,419 --> 00:07:02,547
- Sekali lagi.
<i>- Itulah asal-usul</i>

100
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:05,341
<i>- penubuhan Kasut Ideal.</i>
- Satu, dua, tiga.

101
00:07:06,259 --> 00:07:08,970
Kasut Ideal?
Maksud mak cik, Kasut Ideal itu?

102
00:07:09,053 --> 00:07:11,305
Ya, itulah dia.

103
00:07:12,098 --> 00:07:13,182
Yakah?

104
00:07:13,266 --> 00:07:15,977
Ini kasut tumit tinggi Kasut Ideal.

105
00:07:17,395 --> 00:07:18,646
Kasut itu.

106
00:07:18,729 --> 00:07:22,733
Itu antara kasut terlaris kami.
Kami dah jual sejak 1981.

107
00:07:24,110 --> 00:07:25,653
Kamu pandai pilih kasut.

108
00:07:26,904 --> 00:07:27,905
Wah.

109
00:07:28,573 --> 00:07:30,616
Mak cik memang diam-diam ubi berisi.

110
00:07:32,243 --> 00:07:35,663
Tapi kenapa mak cik berhenti kerja?

111
00:07:35,746 --> 00:07:37,248
Mak cik nampak sihat lagi.

112
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:42,211
Ada benda lebih penting daripada kerja.

113
00:07:43,796 --> 00:07:45,173
Selepas itu,

114
00:07:45,882 --> 00:07:50,386
kami bertiga buka kedai
dengan bajet kecil,

115
00:07:50,470 --> 00:07:53,681
tapi kami yakin dengan produk kami.

116
00:08:40,770 --> 00:08:44,148
- Cantiknya.
<i>- Kasut kami</i>

117
00:08:44,232 --> 00:08:46,609
<i>mula memenuhi rak pameran.</i>

118
00:08:47,944 --> 00:08:51,781
<i>Makin lama,</i>
<i>makin ramai orang suka produk kami.</i>

119
00:08:51,864 --> 00:08:53,199
Satu, dua, tiga.

120
00:08:54,116 --> 00:08:57,537
- Senyum sikit.
<i>- Kami bersengkang mata buat kasut,</i>

121
00:08:57,620 --> 00:08:59,789
<i>tapi kami tak boleh berhenti senyum.</i>

122
00:08:59,872 --> 00:09:00,873
KASUT IDEAL

123
00:09:00,957 --> 00:09:02,124
Rapat sikit.

124
00:09:02,208 --> 00:09:03,876
Satu, dua, tiga.

125
00:09:08,839 --> 00:09:11,217
<i>Ketika itu juga mak cik dapat tahu</i>

126
00:09:11,300 --> 00:09:16,264
<i>Seon Hwa tinggalkan anak dia</i>
<i>yang baru lahir di Korea Utara.</i>

127
00:09:16,806 --> 00:09:17,807
Awak buat apa?

128
00:09:19,183 --> 00:09:20,726
Saya buat hajat.

129
00:09:21,352 --> 00:09:25,022
Supaya dapat jumpa anak saya
di Korea Utara lagi.

130
00:09:30,903 --> 00:09:32,280
Saya pun nak doakan

131
00:09:32,863 --> 00:09:34,615
hajat awak tercapai.

132
00:09:36,117 --> 00:09:37,118
Saya pun.

133
00:09:39,787 --> 00:09:43,541
<i>Kami rasa kami dah berjaya.</i>

134
00:09:44,250 --> 00:09:45,751
<i>Tak perlu takut apa-apa.</i>

135
00:09:55,219 --> 00:09:56,220
<i>Sampailah</i>

136
00:09:57,388 --> 00:09:59,181
<i>Seon Hwa ditahan.</i>

137
00:10:01,684 --> 00:10:03,477
Dia dituduh menjadi perisik.

138
00:10:04,854 --> 00:10:05,855
Rupa-rupanya,

139
00:10:07,315 --> 00:10:09,483
Seon Hwa hantar duit ke Korea Utara.

140
00:10:12,278 --> 00:10:13,279
Lepaskan saya!

141
00:10:13,904 --> 00:10:17,658
<i>Dia jelaskan yang duit itu</i>
<i>untuk keluarga dia di Utara.</i>

142
00:10:17,742 --> 00:10:20,494
- Tunggu. Lepaskan!
- Dia tak bersalah.

143
00:10:20,578 --> 00:10:22,788
- Dia bukan perisik.
- Seon Hwa!

144
00:10:22,872 --> 00:10:24,040
<i>Tapi,</i>

145
00:10:25,041 --> 00:10:27,084
<i>kami pula yang terancam.</i>

146
00:10:28,628 --> 00:10:30,838
<i>Mereka soal kalau kami pun terlibat.</i>

147
00:10:31,505 --> 00:10:34,467
<i>Kalau terlibat,</i>
<i>Kasut Ideal akan terus ditutup.</i>

148
00:10:36,385 --> 00:10:39,347
Mak cik dan suami tak boleh cakap apa-apa.

149
00:10:40,848 --> 00:10:43,142
Kalau syarikat kami tutup,

150
00:10:44,101 --> 00:10:47,605
ramai pekerja akan menganggur.

151
00:10:48,272 --> 00:10:50,816
Ditambah dengan keluarga mereka,
beratus orang.

152
00:10:53,444 --> 00:10:54,445
Akhirnya,

153
00:10:55,071 --> 00:10:59,367
kami cuma mampu berharap
dia akan dilepaskan dengan selamat.

154
00:11:01,285 --> 00:11:03,746
Tahun demi tahun berlalu.

155
00:11:04,455 --> 00:11:06,624
Apabila kami lawat dia,

156
00:11:08,042 --> 00:11:09,418
dia

157
00:11:09,502 --> 00:11:11,545
dah mati.

158
00:11:13,839 --> 00:11:18,219
<i>Kami buat kubur untuk dia</i>
<i>di tempat yang nampak Korea Utara</i>

159
00:11:19,178 --> 00:11:21,639
<i>dan tanam bekas abu dia di situ.</i>

160
00:11:22,890 --> 00:11:24,558
<i>Pilu hati mak cik.</i>

161
00:11:26,644 --> 00:11:30,523
<i>Kalaulah kami lawat dia lebih awal…</i>

162
00:11:31,232 --> 00:11:35,694
<i>Kalaulah kami tak fikirkan syarikat saja</i>
<i>dan selamatkan dia…</i>

163
00:11:37,405 --> 00:11:40,741
<i>Mungkin dia masih hidup.</i>

164
00:11:42,618 --> 00:11:46,997
Disebabkan menyesal, kami putuskan

165
00:11:48,499 --> 00:11:51,377
<i>untuk cari anak dia di Korea Utara</i>

166
00:11:51,460 --> 00:11:52,962
<i>dan beri dia bahagian Seon Hwa.</i>

167
00:11:53,045 --> 00:11:54,713
Tolong cari dia.

168
00:11:55,798 --> 00:11:56,757
Maaf.

169
00:11:57,550 --> 00:12:00,344
Tak apa. Terima kasih
sebab bersusah payah.

170
00:12:00,428 --> 00:12:01,429
Maaf.

171
00:12:01,512 --> 00:12:03,764
Ya. Tak apa.

172
00:12:04,473 --> 00:12:05,558
Terima kasih banyak.

173
00:12:06,225 --> 00:12:10,271
<i>Tapi bukan senang nak cari anak dia.</i>

174
00:12:10,354 --> 00:12:11,439
WASIAT

175
00:12:11,522 --> 00:12:13,357
<i>Disebabkan masih risau,</i>

176
00:12:14,233 --> 00:12:18,696
<i>suami saya tulis wasiat</i>
<i>pembahagian harta untuk anak Seon Hwa.</i>

177
00:12:20,156 --> 00:12:24,118
Selepas setahun suami saya meninggal,

178
00:12:24,827 --> 00:12:26,078
akhirnya,

179
00:12:26,162 --> 00:12:29,707
kami jumpa anak dia, Cha Eun Seong.

180
00:12:30,916 --> 00:12:33,210
Tertulis di sini, pewaris kena sediakan

181
00:12:33,294 --> 00:12:35,880
satu pertiga harta
kepada anak lelaki Cik Ryeo Seon Hwa,

182
00:12:35,963 --> 00:12:38,507
Cha Eun Seong,
jika dia ditemui pada bila-bila masa.

183
00:12:38,591 --> 00:12:40,843
Sebahagian besar harta itu
saham Kasut Ideal.

184
00:12:41,427 --> 00:12:44,680
Habislah syarikat
kalau dia dapat satu pertiga.

185
00:12:45,931 --> 00:12:50,227
Sumbangan Cik Ryeo Seon Hwa terhadap
Kasut Ideal dinyatakan sebagai alasan.

186
00:12:51,604 --> 00:12:55,483
Kita boleh menang mudah
kalau mak awak menentang wasiat ini.

187
00:12:55,566 --> 00:12:56,650
Dia kata apa?

188
00:12:57,318 --> 00:13:00,404
Mak saya kata kami patut ikut wasiat ayah.

189
00:13:01,113 --> 00:13:04,742
Dia sendiri beritahu Cha Eun Seong
tentang wasiat ayah saya.

190
00:13:06,452 --> 00:13:07,870
Dari dulu dia begini.

191
00:13:07,953 --> 00:13:10,539
Dia tak boleh duduk senang-lenang

192
00:13:12,166 --> 00:13:14,084
sedangkan Cik Ryeo mati di penjara.

193
00:13:14,168 --> 00:13:17,755
- Terima kasih. Saya beli.
- Sama-sama. Mak cik jual, ya?

194
00:13:18,297 --> 00:13:20,382
<i>Dia tinggal seorang diri di rumah kecil.</i>

195
00:13:21,091 --> 00:13:24,094
<i>Dia berkeras nak jual sayur,</i>
<i>walaupun saya dah larang.</i>

196
00:13:24,178 --> 00:13:25,304
Tengok-tengok sayur.

197
00:13:26,347 --> 00:13:28,307
Biasanya, dia tak kisah saya buat apa.

198
00:13:28,933 --> 00:13:31,602
Tapi dia mengamuk selepas
saya cakap tak nak beri saham itu.

199
00:13:32,186 --> 00:13:35,564
Dia cakap dia sanggup
masuk mahkamah kalau perlu.

200
00:13:37,650 --> 00:13:38,651
Begitu.

201
00:13:39,527 --> 00:13:41,070
Cukup setakat ini dulu.

202
00:13:41,153 --> 00:13:43,405
Kami kena semak dengan terperinci lagi,

203
00:13:43,489 --> 00:13:45,282
tapi wasiat si mati ini wujud

204
00:13:45,366 --> 00:13:48,410
dan mak awak nekad nak laksanakan wasiat.

205
00:13:48,494 --> 00:13:50,079
Memang kena buat perbicaraan.

206
00:13:50,162 --> 00:13:53,082
Jadi, kita kena menang kes ini.

207
00:14:00,631 --> 00:14:03,342
Kenapa tak cuba pujuk anak mak cik?

208
00:14:04,009 --> 00:14:07,972
Kalau begini, mak cik terpaksa
lawan anak mak cik di mahkamah.

209
00:14:08,889 --> 00:14:10,516
Dua-dua rugi.

210
00:14:10,599 --> 00:14:13,185
Puas mak cik pujuk dia.

211
00:14:13,769 --> 00:14:15,271
Dia keras kepala.

212
00:14:15,854 --> 00:14:17,064
Saya faham kenapa.

213
00:14:17,731 --> 00:14:21,819
Saya tak rasa anak mak cik boleh terima.

214
00:14:22,319 --> 00:14:25,155
Melainkan mak cik bertolak ansur
dan kurangkan jumlah bahagian.

215
00:14:25,239 --> 00:14:27,199
Mak cik tak nak bertolak ansur.

216
00:14:27,283 --> 00:14:29,285
Mak cik tak nak kurangkan jumlah bahagian.

217
00:14:29,994 --> 00:14:32,413
Biarlah masuk mahkamah pun.

218
00:14:32,997 --> 00:14:35,040
Mak cik nak ikut wasiat suami.

219
00:14:35,749 --> 00:14:37,084
Tapi…

220
00:14:37,167 --> 00:14:38,419
Okey.

221
00:14:38,502 --> 00:14:40,588
Baiklah, mak cik.

222
00:14:41,171 --> 00:14:43,257
Mak cik balik dulu.

223
00:14:43,340 --> 00:14:46,635
Kami telefon mak cik
selepas semak dokumen.

224
00:14:47,761 --> 00:14:48,637
Kejap.

225
00:14:50,681 --> 00:14:51,765
Nah.

226
00:14:53,267 --> 00:14:56,562
Ada dokumen dan gambar
Seon Hwa di dalam sampul ini.

227
00:14:56,645 --> 00:14:59,899
Nombor mak cik pun ada.

228
00:15:00,524 --> 00:15:04,570
Mak cik harap sangat
dapat tunaikan janji suami.

229
00:15:07,615 --> 00:15:08,699
Kami cuba yang terbaik.

230
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:11,994
Oh, ya.

231
00:15:12,077 --> 00:15:14,330
Kami kena tahu tentang suami mak cik

232
00:15:14,413 --> 00:15:16,874
untuk persiapan perbicaraan.

233
00:15:17,499 --> 00:15:20,127
Boleh saya tahu nama dan tarikh lahir dia?

234
00:15:20,210 --> 00:15:22,087
Nama dia

235
00:15:22,630 --> 00:15:24,006
Kang Dong-sik.

236
00:15:25,049 --> 00:15:29,845
Dia lahir pada 1 Mac 1953.

237
00:15:31,722 --> 00:15:33,223
Tolong mak cik, ya?

238
00:15:45,110 --> 00:15:46,654
WASIAT

239
00:16:10,386 --> 00:16:11,553
Helo, pak cik.

240
00:16:12,096 --> 00:16:13,013
Apa khabar?

241
00:16:13,097 --> 00:16:17,142
Nama pak cik Kang Dong-sik, tukang kasut.

242
00:16:17,226 --> 00:16:19,061
Saya Peguam Shin I-rang.

243
00:16:19,144 --> 00:16:21,230
Ini Peguam Han Na-hyun.

244
00:16:23,065 --> 00:16:25,442
Helo, saya Peguam Han Na-hyun.

245
00:16:25,526 --> 00:16:27,820
Aduh. Pak cik di sinilah.

246
00:16:29,655 --> 00:16:32,533
- Lupa. Kamu tak nampak pak cik.
- Dia di situ.

247
00:16:33,367 --> 00:16:34,952
Selamat berkenalan.

248
00:16:35,035 --> 00:16:36,537
Dia kata selamat berkenalan.

249
00:16:37,287 --> 00:16:39,790
Pak cik tengok,

250
00:16:39,873 --> 00:16:42,126
kamu jenis yang tak kisah.

251
00:16:42,209 --> 00:16:46,130
Kamu suka praktikal, tapi gaya kena ada.

252
00:16:47,256 --> 00:16:50,509
Kamu suka duduk sambil silangkan kaki.

253
00:16:51,385 --> 00:16:53,512
Macam mana pak cik tahu?

254
00:16:54,388 --> 00:16:57,349
Tengok kasut saja,
boleh tahu semuanya tentang seseorang.

255
00:16:58,684 --> 00:17:02,896
Kamu pakai kasut tak selesa itu
sampai haus tumitnya.

256
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:05,315
Maknanya, kamu jenis yang tak kisah.

257
00:17:05,983 --> 00:17:07,860
Itu kasut jahitan mesin

258
00:17:07,943 --> 00:17:10,112
dengan kulit sintetik,

259
00:17:10,195 --> 00:17:13,323
tapi kamu pilih reka bentuk klasik.

260
00:17:13,991 --> 00:17:16,535
Maknanya, cita rasa kamu boleh tahan.

261
00:17:16,618 --> 00:17:17,953
Aduh.

262
00:17:18,037 --> 00:17:22,791
Tumit kanan lebih banyak haus
daripada tumit kiri.

263
00:17:22,875 --> 00:17:25,794
Pelvis kamu tak sama panjang
sebab kerap silangkan kaki.

264
00:17:26,295 --> 00:17:29,715
Tapi tak serius pun. Jangan risau.

265
00:17:30,382 --> 00:17:32,676
Hebat.

266
00:17:34,636 --> 00:17:36,013
Apa? Dia kata apa?

267
00:17:37,097 --> 00:17:40,392
Semua tekaan dia tentang diri saya betul
dengan tengok kasut saja.

268
00:17:42,561 --> 00:17:45,564
Macam mana dengan mak cik tadi?

269
00:17:46,565 --> 00:17:48,067
Pak cik boleh rasa

270
00:17:48,609 --> 00:17:52,946
dia rajin dan merendah diri
berdasarkan kasut dia.

271
00:17:55,491 --> 00:17:58,118
Dia tak kenal mak cik tadi.

272
00:17:59,536 --> 00:18:02,414
Boleh beri saya gambar
yang mak cik beri tadi?

273
00:18:03,248 --> 00:18:05,250
Macam mana kalau dia rasuk awak?

274
00:18:05,834 --> 00:18:08,337
Kita kena tolong dia pulihkan ingatan.

275
00:18:09,505 --> 00:18:13,300
Dia tak nampak macam orang jahat.
Rasanya tak apa kalau dia rasuk saya.

276
00:18:24,895 --> 00:18:27,564
KASUT IDEAL

277
00:18:38,951 --> 00:18:39,827
Aduh.

278
00:18:40,702 --> 00:18:41,745
Dah lewat.

279
00:18:44,123 --> 00:18:47,751
Mana budak di sini tadi?

280
00:18:49,294 --> 00:18:51,964
Maaf, pak cik nak tanya sikit.

281
00:18:52,589 --> 00:18:55,175
Di mana hentian bas terdekat?

282
00:18:55,759 --> 00:18:57,177
Pak cik nak ke mana?

283
00:18:57,261 --> 00:18:59,847
Pak cik nak ke Malli-dong, buat kasut.

284
00:19:00,639 --> 00:19:04,351
Kasihan pelanggan pak cik
kalau kasut mereka tak sempat siap.

285
00:19:04,434 --> 00:19:05,602
Habislah.

286
00:19:07,271 --> 00:19:08,397
Pak cik.

287
00:19:09,356 --> 00:19:11,525
Malli-dong dah tak macam dulu.

288
00:19:12,109 --> 00:19:14,862
Apa yang dah tak macam dulu?

289
00:19:17,030 --> 00:19:18,574
Macam mana nak cakap…

290
00:19:18,657 --> 00:19:19,700
Adik.

291
00:19:19,783 --> 00:19:21,660
Pak cik minta maaf,

292
00:19:21,743 --> 00:19:24,246
tapi pak cik tak sempat
dengar cerita kamu.

293
00:19:25,747 --> 00:19:27,791
Bagi pelanggan pak cik,

294
00:19:28,584 --> 00:19:30,252
produk pak cik bukan sekadar kasut.

295
00:19:30,878 --> 00:19:33,297
Itu pendorong kejayaan

296
00:19:33,380 --> 00:19:35,716
dan peneman hidup baru mereka.

297
00:19:38,218 --> 00:19:41,471
Aduh, pak cik dah lewat.

298
00:19:41,555 --> 00:19:44,016
Saya memang ada hal di sana.

299
00:19:44,099 --> 00:19:45,100
Saya teman pak cik.

300
00:19:45,184 --> 00:19:47,728
Okey, jom pergi.

301
00:19:53,108 --> 00:19:58,238
BANGUNAN OKCHEON

302
00:20:08,248 --> 00:20:10,500
Pak cik, tunggu di dalam kereta sekejap.

303
00:20:10,584 --> 00:20:11,835
Okey.

304
00:20:47,704 --> 00:20:48,956
Aduh.

305
00:20:58,757 --> 00:21:00,300
- Adik.
- Ya?

306
00:21:00,384 --> 00:21:03,053
- Boleh pak cik tanya sikit?
- Ya.

307
00:21:03,637 --> 00:21:07,307
Pak cik nak ke Malli-dong. Naik bas apa?

308
00:21:07,391 --> 00:21:11,186
Bas 0411 terus pergi ke sana.

309
00:21:12,938 --> 00:21:14,273
Itu basnya.

310
00:21:19,569 --> 00:21:20,988
Terima kasih.

311
00:21:21,071 --> 00:21:22,030
Ya.

312
00:21:28,161 --> 00:21:29,371
Tunggu!

313
00:21:47,681 --> 00:21:50,642
BAS 0411

314
00:21:52,936 --> 00:21:54,563
JALAN KASUT BUATAN TANGAN MALLI-DONG

315
00:21:57,607 --> 00:22:00,152
Encik, saya nak ke jalan
kasut buatan tangan Malli-dong.

316
00:22:00,235 --> 00:22:01,236
Okey.

317
00:22:13,623 --> 00:22:15,709
Inilah tempatnya.

318
00:22:18,128 --> 00:22:19,713
Selamat datang.

319
00:22:29,806 --> 00:22:32,225
Peliknya.

320
00:22:34,269 --> 00:22:36,146
Sepatutnya di sinilah.

321
00:22:36,813 --> 00:22:38,148
Tumpang tanya.

322
00:22:38,815 --> 00:22:40,400
Encik cari apa?

323
00:22:44,321 --> 00:22:45,822
Boleh saya bantu?

324
00:22:45,906 --> 00:22:49,284
Bukan, ini bengkel pak cik.

325
00:22:49,367 --> 00:22:51,286
Apa benda yang berkilat ini?

326
00:22:51,369 --> 00:22:52,662
Encik siapa?

327
00:22:52,746 --> 00:22:55,373
Pak cik buat kasut.

328
00:22:55,957 --> 00:22:57,959
- Mana kasut pak cik?
- Keluar.

329
00:22:58,043 --> 00:23:00,253
Tak, ini bengkel pak cik.

330
00:23:00,337 --> 00:23:02,839
- Tak ada bengkel di sini. Keluar.
- Kenapa tolak-tolak?

331
00:23:07,219 --> 00:23:08,887
Sepatutnya di sinilah.

332
00:24:00,230 --> 00:24:01,648
Peguam Shin!

333
00:25:36,993 --> 00:25:39,246
Okey, cuba pakai.

334
00:25:46,211 --> 00:25:47,295
Maaf.

335
00:25:48,505 --> 00:25:50,715
Saya ingat dia boleh ingat apa-apa

336
00:25:51,216 --> 00:25:53,551
kalau saya bawa dia keluar
dan tengok sendiri.

337
00:25:55,011 --> 00:25:56,638
Saya tak patut bawa dia keluar.

338
00:25:59,557 --> 00:26:00,433
Maaf.

339
00:26:01,977 --> 00:26:03,895
Kamu kenal pak cik?

340
00:26:26,668 --> 00:26:29,129
Kasihan pak cik keseorangan selama ini.

341
00:26:33,800 --> 00:26:35,635
Biar saya tolong pak cik.

342
00:26:59,117 --> 00:27:02,704
FIRMA GUAMAN SHIN I-RANG

343
00:27:07,667 --> 00:27:09,461
Awak nak buat apa dengan kes ini?

344
00:27:09,544 --> 00:27:12,672
Saya rasa kita patut
minta jumlah yang adil.

345
00:27:13,673 --> 00:27:14,841
Awak rasa begitu?

346
00:27:17,010 --> 00:27:21,931
Saya sebenarnya nak tolong dia
laksanakan wasiat suami dia.

347
00:27:24,559 --> 00:27:25,810
Tak boleh, bukan?

348
00:27:30,648 --> 00:27:32,484
Tapi awak tetap akan cuba habis-habisan.

349
00:27:36,988 --> 00:27:38,198
Saya faham sekarang.

350
00:27:38,990 --> 00:27:40,700
Saya pun kena berusaha.

351
00:27:41,284 --> 00:27:43,036
Awak nak tolong saya?

352
00:27:43,620 --> 00:27:46,164
Kita kongsi pejabat ini
dan awak nak lawan Taebaek.

353
00:27:46,956 --> 00:27:49,084
Kejamlah kalau biarkan awak lawan seorang.

354
00:27:49,626 --> 00:27:52,212
Tapi kita bahagi
yuran kontingensi sama rata.

355
00:27:56,925 --> 00:27:57,801
Setuju.

356
00:28:12,982 --> 00:28:16,528
Ayah. Ayah beri kes Kasut Ideal
kepada orang lain?

357
00:28:17,112 --> 00:28:17,946
Ya.

358
00:28:18,530 --> 00:28:21,324
Kenapa? Saya sendiri
dah jumpa CEO Kang Ji-hoon.

359
00:28:21,408 --> 00:28:23,910
Shin I-rang dan Han Na-hyun
peguam pihak satu lagi.

360
00:28:25,745 --> 00:28:26,621
Jadi?

361
00:28:30,166 --> 00:28:32,502
Perasaan peribadi boleh jejaskan
pertimbangan peguam.

362
00:28:32,585 --> 00:28:34,796
Jadi, ayah suruh orang lain ambil alih.

363
00:28:34,879 --> 00:28:37,966
Tak. Saya tak ada perasaan peribadi.

364
00:28:39,384 --> 00:28:40,385
Biar saya buat.

365
00:28:41,094 --> 00:28:43,805
Saya nak buktikan diri sendiri.

366
00:29:00,238 --> 00:29:01,489
Maksudnya,

367
00:29:01,573 --> 00:29:03,783
dulu pak cik tinggal di sini?

368
00:29:06,035 --> 00:29:08,037
Pak cik tak ingat,

369
00:29:09,581 --> 00:29:11,833
tapi macam biasa nampak.

370
00:29:14,836 --> 00:29:16,421
BILIK KERJA

371
00:29:43,656 --> 00:29:45,074
Ini…

372
00:29:45,158 --> 00:29:46,618
Apa benda ini…

373
00:29:50,580 --> 00:29:52,999
Apa? Pak cik ingat apa-apa?

374
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:56,836
Apa benda ini?

375
00:29:58,838 --> 00:30:00,256
Ini…

376
00:30:05,887 --> 00:30:08,264
barang lama suami mak cik.

377
00:30:08,348 --> 00:30:10,350
Mak cik tak sampai hati nak buang.

378
00:30:14,562 --> 00:30:16,397
Banyak juga barang lama pak cik.

379
00:30:16,481 --> 00:30:17,941
Baguslah.

380
00:30:20,235 --> 00:30:22,237
Semua ini dah lama.

381
00:30:32,080 --> 00:30:34,958
I-rang, awak buat apa?

382
00:30:35,041 --> 00:30:37,961
Jangan pakai kasut begini!

383
00:30:38,545 --> 00:30:39,546
Pak cik.

384
00:30:39,629 --> 00:30:42,757
Kasut itu mudah dipakai.

385
00:30:42,841 --> 00:30:44,884
Apa masalahnya kalau mudah dipakai?

386
00:30:45,635 --> 00:30:46,970
Tak ada kelas!

387
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:48,847
Buang saja!

388
00:30:49,764 --> 00:30:51,933
- Aduh.
- I-rang!

389
00:30:52,016 --> 00:30:53,977
Biar betul? Ini tingkat lima!

390
00:30:54,060 --> 00:30:55,311
Aduh!

391
00:30:57,063 --> 00:31:00,108
Ini ringkasan pertikaian
wasiat Kang Ji-hoon.

392
00:31:01,776 --> 00:31:03,987
"Wasiat. Saya, Kang Dong-sik,
tinggalkan ini sebagai wasiat terakhir."

393
00:31:04,070 --> 00:31:07,532
Fokus pada tarikh ini.

394
00:31:07,615 --> 00:31:10,159
Itu kena disemak.
Saya serahkan kepada Peguam Oh.

395
00:31:10,243 --> 00:31:11,870
Maaf. Saya nak tanya sikit.

396
00:31:11,953 --> 00:31:13,162
- Ya?
- Pak cik…

397
00:31:14,205 --> 00:31:16,040
kenal mereka ini?

398
00:31:16,124 --> 00:31:17,333
KASUT IDEAL

399
00:31:17,959 --> 00:31:19,252
Tak, pak cik tak kenal.

400
00:31:20,628 --> 00:31:22,922
Okey. Terima kasih.

401
00:31:26,885 --> 00:31:29,137
KASUT IDEAL

402
00:31:35,727 --> 00:31:36,811
Helo.

403
00:31:42,442 --> 00:31:44,903
Pak cik kenal mereka ini?

404
00:32:05,298 --> 00:32:06,299
Jom.

405
00:32:16,809 --> 00:32:18,061
IKLAN 2010
IKLAN 2015

406
00:32:21,773 --> 00:32:23,066
KENAPA ORANG KOREA DULU TINGGALKAN WASIAT

407
00:32:23,858 --> 00:32:25,193
TESTIMONI
KANG JI-HOON, CEO KASUT IDEAL

408
00:32:25,276 --> 00:32:28,863
Kita dah habis tengok kawasan
dan kumpulkan bahan.

409
00:32:29,739 --> 00:32:32,533
Apa kata kita jumpa En. Cha Eun Seong,
anak Cik Ryeo Seon Hwa?

410
00:32:33,451 --> 00:32:34,494
Beri sini!

411
00:32:35,161 --> 00:32:36,913
Pak cik tak suka kasut itu!

412
00:32:37,413 --> 00:32:39,832
- Tanggalkan sebelah lagi!
- Peguam Han, tahan dia!

413
00:32:39,916 --> 00:32:40,792
Buang!

414
00:32:44,671 --> 00:32:46,005
Terima kasih, Peguam Han!

415
00:32:54,389 --> 00:32:56,265
Wah.

416
00:32:56,349 --> 00:32:58,935
Banyaknya kulit.

417
00:33:03,523 --> 00:33:06,192
- Maaf. Boleh saya tanya sikit?
- Ya?

418
00:33:06,776 --> 00:33:08,820
Saya cari En. Cha Eun Seong.

419
00:33:08,903 --> 00:33:10,905
Bos kami? Dia di situ.

420
00:33:11,614 --> 00:33:12,740
Bos.

421
00:33:21,708 --> 00:33:23,793
Lewat kamu makan hari ini.

422
00:33:23,876 --> 00:33:25,503
Tak elok makan lewat.

423
00:33:25,586 --> 00:33:27,755
Kamu boleh saja datang bila-bila.

424
00:33:27,839 --> 00:33:29,007
Okey?

425
00:33:29,590 --> 00:33:31,426
Makanlah.

426
00:33:31,509 --> 00:33:33,094
Baik, mak cik.

427
00:33:33,678 --> 00:33:35,388
- Makanlah.
- Terima kasih.

428
00:33:37,432 --> 00:33:38,891
Setiap hari saya makan di sini.

429
00:33:39,600 --> 00:33:40,810
Kamu boleh makan mi?

430
00:33:40,893 --> 00:33:43,104
Saya boleh makan apa saja.

431
00:33:48,484 --> 00:33:49,819
Sedapnya.

432
00:33:49,902 --> 00:33:50,903
Sedap.

433
00:33:58,453 --> 00:33:59,787
Saya okey saja.

434
00:34:00,413 --> 00:34:01,831
Kamu boleh tanya apa-apa.

435
00:34:02,457 --> 00:34:05,543
Bila awak datang ke Korea?

436
00:34:06,169 --> 00:34:07,754
Saya dengar awak orang Korea Utara.

437
00:34:08,421 --> 00:34:09,338
Betul.

438
00:34:10,298 --> 00:34:13,843
Saya lahir di Hamgyong dan terpisah
dengan mak semasa umur setahun.

439
00:34:13,926 --> 00:34:17,013
Selepas mak cik meninggal,
saya ke sini lebih sepuluh tahun lepas.

440
00:34:17,597 --> 00:34:21,059
Macam mana awak
boleh buat kerja warnakan kulit?

441
00:34:22,143 --> 00:34:24,145
Satu kampung saya kerja warnakan kulit.

442
00:34:24,228 --> 00:34:26,189
Semua ahli keluarga dan saudara.

443
00:34:28,900 --> 00:34:31,778
Apabila dengar mak saya pun kerja itu,

444
00:34:33,154 --> 00:34:34,572
remuk hati saya.

445
00:34:35,948 --> 00:34:39,619
Apa yang awak tahu tentang mak awak?

446
00:34:40,203 --> 00:34:43,706
Saya dengar dia selalu hantar duit
kepada keluarga saya di Utara

447
00:34:43,790 --> 00:34:46,417
dan cuba bawa kami keluar.

448
00:34:46,501 --> 00:34:50,004
Dia terputus hubungan dengan kami
apabila kami sampai di China.

449
00:34:54,133 --> 00:34:55,676
<i>Kita dengar kisah seterusnya.</i>

450
00:34:56,260 --> 00:34:59,388
<i>"Hari ini ulang tahun kematian pertama</i>

451
00:34:59,472 --> 00:35:01,599
<i>isteri tersayang saya."</i>

452
00:35:02,391 --> 00:35:05,728
<i>"Saya cuba kawal perasaan demi anak-anak,</i>

453
00:35:05,812 --> 00:35:07,855
<i>tapi bukan senang."</i>

454
00:35:08,815 --> 00:35:11,818
<i>"Setiap kali saya dengar</i>
<i>lagu yang dia suka,</i>

455
00:35:11,901 --> 00:35:14,320
<i>lalu di tempat</i>
<i>yang kami kerap jalan bersama,</i>

456
00:35:15,154 --> 00:35:17,448
<i>atau nampak makanan yang kami suka,</i>

457
00:35:18,032 --> 00:35:19,450
<i>saya teringat isteri saya."</i>

458
00:35:20,201 --> 00:35:22,078
<i>"Saya rindu dia…"</i>

459
00:35:24,038 --> 00:35:26,707
Dia tak tahu pun mak dia dah meninggal.

460
00:35:27,291 --> 00:35:28,584
Kasihan dia.

461
00:35:30,336 --> 00:35:32,505
Mungkin mak cik tak sampai hati nak cakap

462
00:35:33,089 --> 00:35:35,007
yang mak dia dah mati.

463
00:35:36,092 --> 00:35:38,594
Kita kena beritahu dia
kalau ada peluang nanti.

464
00:35:51,190 --> 00:35:54,193
BBQ KEDAI DAGING DUB-DUB

465
00:35:55,570 --> 00:35:57,947
Awak masuk dulu.
Saya masuk selepas letak lori.

466
00:35:58,030 --> 00:35:59,115
Sekejap.

467
00:36:04,162 --> 00:36:05,413
Apa ini?

468
00:36:13,337 --> 00:36:14,839
SHIN I-RANG

469
00:36:15,965 --> 00:36:18,384
Bukankah ini nombor telefon awak?

470
00:36:19,218 --> 00:36:20,678
Kalau awak hilang lagi.

471
00:36:22,972 --> 00:36:25,850
- Peguam Han.
- Senang sikit nak cari awak.

472
00:36:27,393 --> 00:36:28,811
Terus masuk nanti.

473
00:36:31,397 --> 00:36:35,943
BANGUNAN OKCHEON

474
00:36:43,701 --> 00:36:45,536
Cinta muda-mudi.

475
00:36:47,997 --> 00:36:50,208
Kami tak ada apa-apa.

476
00:36:50,291 --> 00:36:52,668
Hantu boleh nampak semuanya.

477
00:37:11,979 --> 00:37:13,231
Betul.

478
00:37:15,942 --> 00:37:18,653
<i>Inilah cinta</i>

479
00:37:55,564 --> 00:37:57,858
<i>Apa patut aku buat?</i>

480
00:37:58,359 --> 00:38:01,946
<i>Jika kau tiba-tiba tinggalkan aku</i>

481
00:38:36,981 --> 00:38:39,233
BILIK KERJA

482
00:39:36,040 --> 00:39:38,000
Sayangnya.

483
00:39:38,084 --> 00:39:41,003
Dia paling sesuai jadi suami kau.

484
00:39:45,508 --> 00:39:46,967
Hebatnya dia.

485
00:39:50,638 --> 00:39:52,640
KEPADA DONG-SIK
…SAYA TAK BOLEH PENDAM PERASAAN LAGI…

486
00:40:07,571 --> 00:40:11,325
COKLAT DAEUN

487
00:41:17,975 --> 00:41:19,560
TAHNIAH ATAS FIRMA BARU HAN NA-HYUN

488
00:41:21,312 --> 00:41:22,730
Apa aku buat di sini?

489
00:41:25,733 --> 00:41:27,151
Sedarlah.

490
00:41:32,156 --> 00:41:34,158
SEOUL
BEROPERASI

491
00:41:35,784 --> 00:41:38,746
Hai, Na-hyun. Kamu masih di pejabat?

492
00:41:39,246 --> 00:41:43,250
Mak suruh ayah hantar bekal makanan
untuk kamu dan Peguam Shin.

493
00:41:43,792 --> 00:41:46,253
Tapi tak ada tempat nak letak kereta.

494
00:41:46,795 --> 00:41:48,422
Okey, kamu turun, ya?

495
00:41:48,506 --> 00:41:49,798
Jumpa nanti.

496
00:41:49,882 --> 00:41:51,008
Alamak.

497
00:41:55,804 --> 00:41:56,805
Aduh.

498
00:42:05,272 --> 00:42:06,398
Apa jadi?

499
00:42:06,482 --> 00:42:07,608
Aduh. Pak cik minta maaf.

500
00:42:07,691 --> 00:42:09,193
Pak cik tak tengok depan?

501
00:42:09,276 --> 00:42:11,320
Pak cik minta maaf.

502
00:42:11,403 --> 00:42:12,571
Aduh.

503
00:42:13,572 --> 00:42:16,283
Harga bampar ini saja
sama macam teksi pak cik.

504
00:42:16,909 --> 00:42:17,910
Pak cik minta maaf.

505
00:42:19,328 --> 00:42:20,204
Pak cik mabuk?

506
00:42:20,788 --> 00:42:22,206
Taklah.

507
00:42:22,289 --> 00:42:23,290
Ayah?

508
00:42:23,832 --> 00:42:25,084
Ya.

509
00:42:28,337 --> 00:42:29,380
Aduh.

510
00:42:29,964 --> 00:42:31,423
Teruk juga kemiknya.

511
00:42:31,507 --> 00:42:33,926
Tak apa, calar sikit saja.

512
00:42:34,009 --> 00:42:35,344
- Apa?
- Bercalar saja.

513
00:42:35,427 --> 00:42:36,762
Tak, pak cik langgar…

514
00:42:36,845 --> 00:42:38,305
Memang dah kemik pun.

515
00:42:38,389 --> 00:42:40,808
Tak apa. Pak cik luka di mana-mana?

516
00:42:40,891 --> 00:42:42,810
Pak cik okey, tapi kamu…

517
00:42:42,893 --> 00:42:45,271
Saya okey, sebab saya muda dan kuat.

518
00:42:45,354 --> 00:42:47,273
- Ayah.
- Na-hyun.

519
00:42:48,274 --> 00:42:49,858
- En. Yang?
- Hai.

520
00:42:50,442 --> 00:42:52,194
Kamu kenal dia?

521
00:42:53,696 --> 00:42:57,199
Pak cik mesti ayah Peguam Han.

522
00:42:58,576 --> 00:43:02,371
Saya Rakan Kongsi Urusan Yang Do-kyung
di pejabat lama dia.

523
00:43:03,038 --> 00:43:05,958
Aduh, kemik teruk kereta dia.

524
00:43:06,750 --> 00:43:08,419
- Aduh.
- Apa jadi?

525
00:43:08,502 --> 00:43:11,714
Ayah pegang bekal makanan
sebab takut terjatuh, tapi…

526
00:43:13,507 --> 00:43:16,218
Maaf. Kita selesaikan dengan insurans.

527
00:43:16,302 --> 00:43:18,637
- Awak cedera?
- Tak. Saya tak cedera.

528
00:43:18,721 --> 00:43:20,723
- Saya yang langgar.
- Apa?

529
00:43:21,390 --> 00:43:23,601
Tak, ayah yang langgar.

530
00:43:23,684 --> 00:43:26,061
Pak cik merepek apa?
Saya peguam kemalangan kereta.

531
00:43:26,145 --> 00:43:28,105
Saya yang langgar, habis cerita.

532
00:43:28,689 --> 00:43:31,567
Tak, Na-hyun.
Ayah yang langgar kereta dia.

533
00:43:32,776 --> 00:43:34,361
Rumit juga situasi ini.

534
00:43:34,445 --> 00:43:36,363
Saya pergi dulu. Jumpa lagi nanti.

535
00:43:36,447 --> 00:43:37,406
Ya.

536
00:43:37,990 --> 00:43:39,199
En. Yang.

537
00:43:39,283 --> 00:43:40,200
Ya?

538
00:43:43,537 --> 00:43:45,748
- Apa itu?
- Tak ada apa.

539
00:43:45,831 --> 00:43:48,917
- Itu untuk saya?
- Tak, untuk orang lain.

540
00:43:49,543 --> 00:43:52,838
Tertulis,
"Tahniah atas firma baru Han Na-hyun."

541
00:43:56,884 --> 00:43:57,801
Aduh.

542
00:43:58,677 --> 00:43:59,887
Entah siapa tulis.

543
00:44:01,263 --> 00:44:02,181
Bukan.

544
00:44:17,905 --> 00:44:18,864
Apa?

545
00:44:26,872 --> 00:44:29,208
Apa aku buat di sini?

546
00:44:31,210 --> 00:44:33,337
Apa aku buat sampai tangan begini?

547
00:44:36,882 --> 00:44:38,676
Mana telefon aku?

548
00:44:40,803 --> 00:44:43,931
Pak cik, ada apa-apa jadi di rumah?

549
00:44:44,515 --> 00:44:46,684
Pak cik buat kasut.

550
00:44:47,267 --> 00:44:48,644
Kasut?

551
00:44:49,603 --> 00:44:50,479
Kasut untuk siapa?

552
00:44:53,524 --> 00:44:55,859
Pak cik tak ingat.

553
00:45:10,416 --> 00:45:11,750
Kenapa tak pakai kasut?

554
00:45:12,960 --> 00:45:15,337
Tak ada apa. Awak lewat.

555
00:45:16,088 --> 00:45:17,965
- Ada hal tadi.
- Okey.

556
00:45:19,758 --> 00:45:21,385
Mana awak dapat pokok itu?

557
00:45:22,428 --> 00:45:23,554
Nak tahu tak?

558
00:45:23,637 --> 00:45:26,348
Rakan Kongsi Urusan Yang
dari Taebaek datang tadi.

559
00:45:26,432 --> 00:45:28,183
- Yang Do-kyung?
- Ya.

560
00:45:29,601 --> 00:45:30,519
Mana Peguam Han?

561
00:45:30,602 --> 00:45:32,688
Dia pergi hantar En. Yang keluar.

562
00:45:32,771 --> 00:45:34,523
Mungkin mereka pergi makan?

563
00:45:36,650 --> 00:45:38,068
Telefonlah kalau nak tahu.

564
00:45:38,152 --> 00:45:41,572
Tak apa, tak perlu telefon dia.

565
00:45:45,951 --> 00:45:50,789
BANGUNAN OKCHEON

566
00:46:02,092 --> 00:46:03,093
SHIN I-RANG

567
00:46:04,470 --> 00:46:06,805
Banyak kerja, bukan?

568
00:46:07,973 --> 00:46:10,309
Maaf. Apa pak cik cakap?

569
00:46:11,018 --> 00:46:14,521
Kita kena hubungkan dua individu berbeza,

570
00:46:15,355 --> 00:46:17,024
licinkan mereka,

571
00:46:17,941 --> 00:46:21,195
kena digilap dari masa ke masa,

572
00:46:21,278 --> 00:46:23,572
sebab itu susah.

573
00:46:24,865 --> 00:46:26,575
Kasut

574
00:46:26,658 --> 00:46:28,118
dan cinta.

575
00:46:30,329 --> 00:46:32,080
Cinta? Pak cik cakap apa?

576
00:46:32,164 --> 00:46:34,708
Hantu tahu semuanya.

577
00:46:37,002 --> 00:46:39,922
Kedua-dua itu sama saja.

578
00:46:40,005 --> 00:46:43,634
Semakin bersinar kalau
semakin banyak jiwa raga dicurahkan.

579
00:46:45,135 --> 00:46:46,512
Tolonglah.

580
00:46:53,727 --> 00:46:54,978
Abang ipar kamu.

581
00:46:55,687 --> 00:46:56,522
Apa?

582
00:46:58,065 --> 00:47:00,609
- I-rang.
- Bong-su?

583
00:47:07,866 --> 00:47:09,117
BBQ KEDAI DAGING DUB-DUB

584
00:47:09,201 --> 00:47:11,787
Peguam Han, ada apa
datang waktu begini…

585
00:47:11,870 --> 00:47:13,789
Awak ke mana? Awak kata nak terus naik.

586
00:47:14,498 --> 00:47:17,626
- Saya…
- Kenapa tak jawab telefon?

587
00:47:17,709 --> 00:47:19,253
Telefon saya hilang…

588
00:47:19,336 --> 00:47:22,548
Lagi satu, kenapa awak balik sendiri?
Kenapa tak tunggu saya?

589
00:47:22,631 --> 00:47:24,174
Risau saya tadi.

590
00:47:25,676 --> 00:47:28,887
Saya dengar awak keluar dengan En. Yang.

591
00:47:28,971 --> 00:47:30,973
- Saya tak nak kacau.
- Kacau?

592
00:47:31,765 --> 00:47:34,935
Tadi ada kemalangan. Saya tinggalkan dia
selepas telefon insurans.

593
00:47:35,727 --> 00:47:37,521
Tak tahu pula awak dah balik.

594
00:47:37,604 --> 00:47:39,856
Saya bawa benda ini
dan cari awak di Malli-dong!

595
00:47:41,942 --> 00:47:42,901
Yakah?

596
00:47:44,069 --> 00:47:46,530
Awak marah?

597
00:47:49,449 --> 00:47:50,993
Saya bukan marah.

598
00:47:51,868 --> 00:47:54,204
Saya letih saja. Kaki pun sakit.

599
00:48:03,338 --> 00:48:04,214
Terima kasih.

600
00:48:06,383 --> 00:48:08,093
Untuk apa? Saya kata saya letih.

601
00:48:08,677 --> 00:48:10,762
Kenapa awak tak faham bahasa?

602
00:48:13,932 --> 00:48:16,685
Maaf. Saya janji tak buat lagi.

603
00:48:17,269 --> 00:48:18,103
Kenapa gelak?

604
00:48:20,063 --> 00:48:20,939
Maaf.

605
00:48:21,023 --> 00:48:22,691
Sikit-sikit, minta maaf.

606
00:48:24,151 --> 00:48:25,402
Tak tahu cakap benda lain?

607
00:48:28,113 --> 00:48:30,741
Itulah. Entah kenapa saya suka minta maaf.

608
00:48:37,831 --> 00:48:39,333
Awak dah makan?

609
00:48:40,292 --> 00:48:41,376
Ingat saya ada masa?

610
00:48:41,918 --> 00:48:44,921
Saya pun belum. Jom makan sekali?

611
00:48:46,798 --> 00:48:47,966
Nak makan apa?

612
00:48:48,550 --> 00:48:50,552
Ada restoran sedap dekat sini.

613
00:49:03,732 --> 00:49:06,068
SUSYI

614
00:49:06,151 --> 00:49:08,737
- Selamat datang!
- Selamat datang!

615
00:49:16,161 --> 00:49:17,454
Mesti awak lapar.

616
00:49:17,537 --> 00:49:19,539
Awak makanlah puas-puas.

617
00:49:20,123 --> 00:49:21,333
Macam buang tabiat pula.

618
00:49:21,958 --> 00:49:22,918
Ini hari istimewa?

619
00:49:23,502 --> 00:49:24,586
Tak,

620
00:49:24,670 --> 00:49:27,589
tapi awak letih hari ini disebabkan saya.

621
00:49:28,548 --> 00:49:29,716
Jangan menyesal.

622
00:49:30,300 --> 00:49:31,551
Saya hantu susyi.

623
00:49:34,137 --> 00:49:35,013
Saya pun.

624
00:49:38,767 --> 00:49:40,477
Mana tuna?

625
00:49:41,103 --> 00:49:42,854
Kita boleh pesan.

626
00:49:42,938 --> 00:49:44,606
- Maaf.
- Ya?

627
00:49:44,690 --> 00:49:46,692
Boleh beri kami dua piring susyi tuna?

628
00:49:46,775 --> 00:49:48,193
- Sekejap.
- Terima kasih.

629
00:49:49,403 --> 00:49:51,822
Macam sedap saja.

630
00:49:53,907 --> 00:49:56,326
- Susyi tuna siap.
- Terima kasih.

631
00:49:57,369 --> 00:49:58,286
Nah.

632
00:50:08,046 --> 00:50:09,548
Sedapnya.

633
00:50:25,105 --> 00:50:26,189
Hantu betul, ya?

634
00:50:30,485 --> 00:50:31,570
Mantap.

635
00:50:37,075 --> 00:50:38,618
Mana kasut mak?

636
00:50:38,702 --> 00:50:41,830
Mak, kasut Heartsping saya pun hilang.

637
00:50:41,913 --> 00:50:45,000
- Peliknya.
- Saya baru nak pakai.

638
00:50:45,709 --> 00:50:47,085
Pak cik.

639
00:50:47,169 --> 00:50:50,922
Sementara tunggu,
pak cik tengok semua kasut ini.

640
00:50:52,257 --> 00:50:54,468
Ini kasut seluruh keluarga kamu.

641
00:50:55,177 --> 00:50:56,178
Ya.

642
00:50:57,637 --> 00:50:59,181
- Saya pergi dulu.
- Okey.

643
00:51:00,223 --> 00:51:01,600
BBQ KEDAI DAGING DUB-DUB

644
00:51:03,268 --> 00:51:04,603
Aduhai.

645
00:51:05,896 --> 00:51:07,647
Kaki awak macam mana?

646
00:51:09,024 --> 00:51:11,193
Fokus pada perbicaraan dulu.

647
00:51:18,074 --> 00:51:19,701
Lama tak jumpa tuan.

648
00:51:20,368 --> 00:51:22,287
Baguslah tuan dah sihat.

649
00:51:22,370 --> 00:51:25,081
Lama betul kita tak jumpa.

650
00:51:25,165 --> 00:51:27,209
Saya sedih awak tinggalkan Taebaek.

651
00:51:27,876 --> 00:51:30,670
Tapi saya lega tengok awak kerja
dengan Peguam Shin.

652
00:51:31,671 --> 00:51:33,757
Okey. Semoga berjaya.

653
00:51:33,840 --> 00:51:34,758
Ya.

654
00:51:43,934 --> 00:51:46,436
Kenapa ayah baik sangat
dengan Shin I-rang?

655
00:51:47,229 --> 00:51:48,146
Yakah?

656
00:51:49,356 --> 00:51:50,649
Tapi,

657
00:51:50,732 --> 00:51:53,985
ayah tak tahu perangai pelik dia.

658
00:52:22,055 --> 00:52:24,266
Kenapa benda ini ada di luar?

659
00:52:41,199 --> 00:52:42,117
Tak mungkin.

660
00:52:45,203 --> 00:52:47,914
BUAT H TERSAYANG, DARIPADA DONG-SIK

661
00:52:55,881 --> 00:52:56,715
Sekejap.

662
00:53:01,803 --> 00:53:07,976
Kita mulakan perbicaraan
Kes 2025-Gahab-1901458.

663
00:53:11,646 --> 00:53:13,315
Mak cik tak sampai lagi.

664
00:53:15,317 --> 00:53:16,234
Itulah.

665
00:53:17,277 --> 00:53:18,278
Mana En. Kang?

666
00:53:18,945 --> 00:53:19,988
Di dalam lori.

667
00:53:20,071 --> 00:53:21,907
Dia tak masuk. Jangan risau.

668
00:53:24,200 --> 00:53:26,786
Perbicaraan ini dijalankan
berikutan saman yang difailkan

669
00:53:26,870 --> 00:53:30,874
oleh Plaintif Kang Ji-hoon,
dengan dakwaan wasiat mendiang bapanya,

670
00:53:30,957 --> 00:53:33,877
Kang Dong-sik, tidak sah
sementara Defendan Chae Jeong-hui,

671
00:53:33,960 --> 00:53:37,547
ibunya, mahu melaksanakan wasiat ini.

672
00:53:38,214 --> 00:53:41,343
Peguam bela, mulakan hujah pembukaan.

673
00:53:47,557 --> 00:53:51,478
Pada 1979, Kang Dong-sik, Chae Jeong-hui
dan Ryeo Seon Hwa membuka Kasut Ideal,

674
00:53:51,561 --> 00:53:56,316
kedai kasut buatan tangan di Malli-dong
dan menjadi pemilik bersama.

675
00:53:57,067 --> 00:54:00,862
Saya dah serahkan dokumen korporat
dan gambar sebagai bukti.

676
00:54:01,321 --> 00:54:02,739
BAHAN BUKTI 2-1, 2-2, 4-1, 4-3

677
00:54:04,324 --> 00:54:07,661
Kemahiran pemprosesan kulit
Cik Ryeo Seon Hwa

678
00:54:07,744 --> 00:54:11,498
menjadi asas perkembangan
perniagaan mereka.

679
00:54:11,581 --> 00:54:15,752
Demi mengiktiraf sumbangannya,
mendiang Pengerusi Kang Dong-sik

680
00:54:15,835 --> 00:54:20,799
mewasiatkan satu pertiga harta
kepada anak lelaki Cik Ryeo.

681
00:54:34,521 --> 00:54:37,691
Oleh itu, sebagai wakil defendan,

682
00:54:37,774 --> 00:54:40,443
saya minta Plaintif Kang Ji-hoon

683
00:54:40,527 --> 00:54:44,572
melaksanakan wasiat
mendiang Pengerusi Kang Dong-sik

684
00:54:45,156 --> 00:54:48,076
dan serahkan satu pertiga harta
kepada anak Cik Ryeo, Cha Eun Seong.

685
00:54:48,159 --> 00:54:49,244
Itu saja.

686
00:55:04,134 --> 00:55:07,470
Kami akan laksanakan wasiat itu…

687
00:55:09,639 --> 00:55:12,559
kalau wasiat pengerusi itu tulen.

688
00:55:13,685 --> 00:55:17,063
Cik Chae Jeong-hui,
isteri mendiang Pengerusi Kang Dong-sik,

689
00:55:17,147 --> 00:55:20,025
dah buktikan yang itu tulisan suami dia.

690
00:55:22,360 --> 00:55:23,236
Betul.

691
00:55:24,612 --> 00:55:26,948
Dengan bantuan
Institut Pemeriksaan Dokumen Korea,

692
00:55:27,032 --> 00:55:28,533
satu analisis terperinci

693
00:55:29,117 --> 00:55:32,912
menunjukkan yang wasiat itu
memang ditulis oleh pengerusi.

694
00:55:32,996 --> 00:55:35,498
Tapi ada satu masalah lain.

695
00:55:37,125 --> 00:55:37,959
Peguam Shin I-rang.

696
00:55:39,002 --> 00:55:41,546
Boleh beritahu saya
bila wasiat ini ditulis?

697
00:55:44,257 --> 00:55:46,885
Kenapa?
Dah tertulis tarikhnya dalam wasiat.

698
00:55:46,968 --> 00:55:49,345
Sila beritahu saya
bila wasiat ini ditulis.

699
00:55:54,684 --> 00:55:57,854
12 Jun 2019.

700
00:55:58,772 --> 00:56:02,150
Betul. Itulah masalahnya.

701
00:56:02,233 --> 00:56:03,485
Kenapa itu masalahnya?

702
00:56:04,319 --> 00:56:08,031
Simptom Alzheimer Pengerusi Kang Dong-sik
makin teruk pada 2021.

703
00:56:08,615 --> 00:56:12,744
Wasiat ini ditulis pada 2019,
dua tahun sebelumnya.

704
00:56:12,827 --> 00:56:16,331
Betulkah wasiat ini ditulis pada 2019?

705
00:56:21,628 --> 00:56:23,129
WASIAT
SAYA, KANG DONG-SIK…

706
00:56:24,422 --> 00:56:26,883
WASIAT

707
00:56:27,467 --> 00:56:31,304
Keputusan analisis dakwat
yang digunakan dalam wasiat menunjukkan

708
00:56:31,387 --> 00:56:34,974
ia ditulis dengan pen founten Napoleon.

709
00:56:35,058 --> 00:56:36,810
Syarikat pen founten ini

710
00:56:36,893 --> 00:56:39,979
tingkatkan kandungan pH dakwat hitamnya

711
00:56:40,063 --> 00:56:44,776
daripada 6.7 kepada 7.2 untuk
tingkatkan kelancaran pada November 2022.

712
00:56:45,527 --> 00:56:46,736
Yang mengejutkan,

713
00:56:47,320 --> 00:56:51,324
kandungan pH dakwat dalam wasiat
yang kononnya ditulis pada Jun 2019 ini,

714
00:56:51,866 --> 00:56:53,326
ialah 7.2.

715
00:56:55,036 --> 00:56:59,040
Maka, wasiat ini
bukan ditulis pada Jun 2019.

716
00:56:59,874 --> 00:57:02,210
Selain itu, pada November 2022,

717
00:57:02,293 --> 00:57:05,171
pengerusi tak cam isterinya

718
00:57:05,255 --> 00:57:07,549
dan juga anaknya sendiri
disebabkan demensia teruk.

719
00:57:08,591 --> 00:57:11,761
Ini lampiran testimoni pakar perubatan.

720
00:57:11,845 --> 00:57:12,971
Bantahan!

721
00:57:13,054 --> 00:57:14,055
Saya nak dengar lagi.

722
00:57:15,098 --> 00:57:16,015
Terima kasih.

723
00:57:16,850 --> 00:57:17,976
Persoalannya,

724
00:57:18,059 --> 00:57:22,605
jika wasiat ini tak ditulis oleh pengerusi
yang penyakitnya semakin parah ketika itu,

725
00:57:23,440 --> 00:57:26,484
siapa yang tulis wasiat ini?

726
00:57:32,740 --> 00:57:35,285
Dengan perisian antipemalsuan dokumen,

727
00:57:35,368 --> 00:57:38,037
kami periksa persamaan antara wasiat

728
00:57:38,121 --> 00:57:40,206
dengan tulisan seseorang.

729
00:57:40,290 --> 00:57:41,207
Keputusannya,

730
00:57:41,791 --> 00:57:45,044
kekerapan penggunaan
kata hubung dan kata ganti nama

731
00:57:45,128 --> 00:57:48,089
serta kedudukan kata kerja
ada padanan lebih 94 peratus.

732
00:57:49,841 --> 00:57:51,342
Orang ini ialah…

733
00:58:05,648 --> 00:58:07,275
COKLAT DAEUN

734
00:58:22,707 --> 00:58:23,750
Dah habis?

735
00:58:23,833 --> 00:58:25,460
Ya, sikit lagi.

736
00:58:28,254 --> 00:58:30,006
Cantiknya.

737
00:58:30,924 --> 00:58:31,925
Cantik, bukan?

738
00:59:17,554 --> 00:59:19,973
Kalau awak waras,

739
00:59:21,182 --> 00:59:24,060
mesti awak setuju dengan saya.

740
00:59:26,020 --> 00:59:26,980
Sayang.

741
00:59:29,190 --> 00:59:31,359
Cakaplah awak setuju.

742
00:59:41,327 --> 00:59:43,913
Okey, pegang pen.

743
00:59:45,290 --> 00:59:46,374
Tulis.

744
00:59:47,292 --> 00:59:48,626
- Tulis?
- Ya.

745
00:59:52,046 --> 00:59:53,006
Tulis apa?

746
00:59:53,756 --> 00:59:55,008
"Wasiat."

747
00:59:58,595 --> 01:00:00,972
"Saya, Kang Dong-sik…"

748
01:00:01,055 --> 01:00:02,640
<i>Saya, Kang Dong-sik…</i>

749
01:00:02,724 --> 01:00:03,850
"…tinggalkan ini…"

750
01:00:03,933 --> 01:00:07,186
<i>…tinggalkan ini sebagai wasiat terakhir.</i>

751
01:00:08,730 --> 01:00:10,189
Apa…

752
01:00:10,273 --> 01:00:11,399
Sayang.

753
01:00:11,482 --> 01:00:13,067
Orang ini ialah…

754
01:00:14,444 --> 01:00:15,737
Cik Chae Jeong-hui.

755
01:00:22,702 --> 01:00:23,870
Dakwaan dia tak masuk akal.

756
01:00:23,953 --> 01:00:26,164
Dia tak ada sebab untuk palsukan wasiat.

757
01:00:26,247 --> 01:00:27,999
Tak. Dia ada satu sebab.

758
01:00:29,000 --> 01:00:31,711
Orang yang laporkan
Cik Ryeo Seon Hwa itu perisik…

759
01:00:32,712 --> 01:00:34,380
- Lepaskan!
- Dia bukan perisik.

760
01:00:34,464 --> 01:00:36,549
Seon Hwa!

761
01:00:36,633 --> 01:00:39,469
…ialah Cik Chae Jeong-hui.

762
01:00:41,638 --> 01:00:43,097
Tak mungkin.

763
01:00:46,643 --> 01:00:48,061
Mengarut saja!

764
01:00:49,354 --> 01:00:50,355
Sayang.

765
01:00:51,814 --> 01:00:54,359
Saya kemukakan dokumen
Agensi Perisikan Tentera.

766
01:00:55,193 --> 01:00:56,527
INFORMAN: CHAE JEONG-HUI

767
01:00:58,154 --> 01:01:00,990
Sayang! Tergamak awak!

768
01:01:01,949 --> 01:01:07,455
Dokumen ini jelas menyatakan
Cik Chae yang laporkan Cik Ryeo Seon Hwa.

769
01:01:07,538 --> 01:01:09,874
Kami tak dimaklumkan tentang bukti ini.

770
01:01:09,957 --> 01:01:11,834
Cik Chae laporkan Cik Ryeo,

771
01:01:11,918 --> 01:01:14,003
tapi selepas Cik Ryeo
meninggal di penjara,

772
01:01:14,087 --> 01:01:17,715
dia cuba tinggalkan harta
kepada anak Cik Ryeo, Cha Eun Seong,

773
01:01:17,799 --> 01:01:19,550
demi menghilangkan rasa bersalahnya,

774
01:01:20,760 --> 01:01:22,929
termasuklah memalsukan wasiat suaminya.

775
01:01:27,308 --> 01:01:28,393
Sayang!

776
01:01:35,525 --> 01:01:37,777
Memandangkan wasiat ini terbukti palsu,

777
01:01:37,860 --> 01:01:40,196
plaintif tidak perlu berkongsi harta

778
01:01:40,279 --> 01:01:41,572
dengan anak Ryeo Seon Hwa…

779
01:01:41,656 --> 01:01:42,824
Jangan, pak cik.

780
01:01:42,907 --> 01:01:45,201
- Bukan sekarang.
- …tiada sebab untuk teruskan.

781
01:01:45,785 --> 01:01:47,036
- Apa…
- Saya mohon…

782
01:01:47,120 --> 01:01:49,330
- Cakap benda betul!
- …supaya perbicaraan

783
01:01:49,414 --> 01:01:50,665
ditamatkan.

784
01:01:52,875 --> 01:01:54,669
Saya yang tulis!

785
01:01:59,716 --> 01:02:00,591
Apa?

786
01:02:00,675 --> 01:02:03,553
Saya tulis wasiat itu!

787
01:02:03,636 --> 01:02:04,595
Saya!

788
01:02:04,679 --> 01:02:06,723
Peguam bela, awak buat apa?

789
01:02:07,348 --> 01:02:10,184
Awak nak dihalau sebab
sumpah bohong dan menghina mahkamah?

790
01:02:10,268 --> 01:02:13,771
Tuan hakim. Dengar cakap saya!

791
01:02:13,855 --> 01:02:14,897
Saya…

792
01:02:14,981 --> 01:02:16,149
Yang Arif!

793
01:02:16,232 --> 01:02:18,484
Peguam Shin I-rang
ada penyakit kronik serius.

794
01:02:19,360 --> 01:02:23,114
Saya mohon mahkamah rehat sebentar
disebabkan penyakit dia.

795
01:02:23,197 --> 01:02:24,991
Rehat sebentar, bukan tamatkan!

796
01:03:00,276 --> 01:03:03,196
BUAT H TERSAYANG, DARIPADA DONG-SIK

797
01:03:12,288 --> 01:03:14,123
Kenapa mak cik laporkan Cik Ryeo?

798
01:03:14,207 --> 01:03:15,541
<i>- Maaf.</i>
<i>- Sayang.</i>

799
01:03:15,625 --> 01:03:17,752
<i>Tapi dia suka orang lain.</i>

800
01:03:17,835 --> 01:03:20,379
<i>Saya nampak awak dengan dia di bengkel.</i>

801
01:03:20,463 --> 01:03:22,173
Seon Hwa!

802
01:03:22,256 --> 01:03:23,257
<i>Kita lepaskan kes ini.</i>

803
01:03:23,341 --> 01:03:26,594
Macam mana kalau Seon Hwa masih hidup?

804
01:03:26,677 --> 01:03:28,054
Semuanya akan berubah.

805
01:03:28,137 --> 01:03:30,056
Cari tempat Ryeo Seon Hwa ditanam cepat.

806
01:03:30,139 --> 01:03:31,641
Ada orang cari awak.

807
01:03:31,724 --> 01:03:33,684
<i>- Lari.</i>
<i>- Seon Hwa.</i>

808
01:03:33,768 --> 01:03:35,353
Itu dia.

809
01:03:35,853 --> 01:03:39,774
Terjemahan sari kata oleh Ika Nurika

